OL,6,FTwo fans attacked a fan and "gave him
OL,7,Fa kicking" in the stands after he
OL,8,Fcelebrated a last-minute winning goal
OL,9,Fin the end.
OL,11,FBrothers Cory Jones, 28, and Steven
OL,12,FJones, 34, punched, kicked, and
OL,13,Fstamped on the victim in an attack
OL,14,Fwhich was caught on camera.
OL,16,FThey have both been handed suspended
OL,17,Fprison sentences and have been given
OL,18,Ffive-year football banning orders.JThe
OL,19,FJones' made a beeline for fan Samuel
OL,20,FEvans who attended the south Wales
OL,21,Fderby at the on 1 April last year.
