OL,6,FIn mitigation, defence barrister
OL,7,FAndrew Taylor said: "The main stadium
OL,8,Fin Cardiff has a designated area for
OL,9,Faway fans. It's segregated and one
OL,10,Fonly needs to travel on the M4 to the
OL,11,Fgames to see the exits and entrances
OL,12,Fof are designated."
OL,14,FIn response Judge Lucy Crowther said:
OL,15,F"Everybody in needs to understand
OL,16,Fwhatever rules and regulations there
OL,17,Fare that does not justify someone
OL,18,Fgetting a kicking because two
OL,19,Fsupporters decide they don't like them
OL,20,Fsitting there and that's what those
OL,21,Fmen did ` they gave him a kicking."
