OL,6,FHe said Steven Jones has a young child
OL,7,Fand works to support his family. The
OL,8,Fbarrister said the brothers had lost
OL,9,Ftheir mother not long before the
OL,10,Fassault and "drank too much" on the
OL,11,Fday of the match.
